<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <title>Wiki searcher</title>
        <style>
            body {
                font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
                margin: 0;
                padding: 0;
            }


            .title-bar {
                background-color: #333;
                color: #fff;
                padding: 10px;
                text-align: center; 
                position: relative; 
            }

            .title-bar h1 {
                margin: 0;
            }

            .dropdown {
                position: absolute;
                top: 100%;
                right: 0;
                background-color: #3d3535;
                border-radius: 5px;
                padding: 20px;
                height: 500px;
                width: 400px;
                display: none; 
            }

            .title-bar:hover .dropdown {
                display: block; 
            }

            .search-bar {
                margin-top: 10px;
                margin-bottom: 10px;
                display: flex;
                justify-content: center; 
            }

            .search-bar form {
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
            }

            .search-bar input[type="text"] {
                padding: 5px;
                border: 1px solid #ccc;
                border-radius: 3px;
                width: 200px;
            }

            .search-bar button {
                padding: 5px 10px;
                background-color: #333;
                color: #fff;
                border: none;
                cursor: pointer;
                margin-left: 10px;
            }

            .button {
                display: inline-block;
                padding: 10px 20px;
                background-color: #333;
                color: #fff;
                text-decoration: none;
                margin-right: 10px;
            }

            .button:hover {
                background-color: #555;
            }

            .button-container {
                margin-top: 20px;
                display: flex;
                justify-content: center; 
            }

            .card-container {
                display: grid;
                grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); 
                grid-gap: 20px;
                margin: 20px;
            }

            .card {
                background-color: #f2f2f2;
                border-radius: 5px;
                padding: 20px;
                text-align: center;
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <div class="title-bar">
            <h1>Wiki searcher</h1>
            <div class="dropdown">
                <h2>Help</h2>
                <p>To start you should write logical query in search panel.</p>
                <p>Example: ((Obama AND Biden) OR Trump)</p>
                <p>If you wait so many times, dont warry, while you wait from internet downloading many information about your qweries.</p>
                <p>After downloading pages you can see cards with title and summary made by AI.</p>
                <p>Why you see this pages?</p>
                <p>You see pages satisfy your query. If you do not see your words in title or summary, that means this words in content.</p>
                <p>Also, on wiki page you can see title, url, main image, summarise by AI, summarise by human and content of page.</p>
                <p>Enjoy!</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="search-bar">
            <form action="/search-result" method="GET">
                <input type="text" name="query" placeholder="Search...">
                <button type="submit">Search</button>
            </form>
        </div>
        
        <div class="button-container">
            <a href="/" class="button">Main</a>
            <a href="/metrics" class="button">Metrics</a>
        </div>
        
        {% for page in json_pages %}
            <div class="card-container">
                <div class="card">
                    <a href="/wiki-page/{{ page['title'] }}">
                        <h2>{{ page["title"] }}</h2>
                    </a>
                    <p>{{ page["Words"] }}</p>
                    <p>{{ page["summary"] }}</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        {% endfor %}
    </body>
</html>